    <string name="about_text">"Fake Text Message allows you to create fake text messages without actually sending them. Just put in a phone number, enter the time/date the text message was expected to arrive, type your message and hit the Fake button! 

The app might work differently on some phones. So, make sure to test the app with a friendly number. 

There are 4 types of messages you can send:
 1)Inbox – fake received SMS
 2)Sent – fake SMS sent successfully to anyone.
 3)Draft – fake SMS saved as draft.
 4)Outbox- fake SMS sent to anyone.
 5)Failed- fake SMS that failed to send."</string>
